*Noću* se odmaram i spremam se za novi dan. (I rest at night and get ready for a new day.)

*Noću* mi se sanjaš u snovima. (You dream of me in my dreams at night.)

Kako provodim *noć*? Provodim je uz knjige i filmove. (How do I spend the night? I spend it with books and movies.)

*Noću* se ugasilo svetlo. (The light went out at night.)

*Noću* se često prepuštam svojim mislima. (I often surrender to my thoughts at night.)